---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Living with the Ghost of Sam - Show Synopsis">
  <div class="synopsis-container">
    <header class="nav-header">
      <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/characters">Characters</a>
        <a href="/episodes">Episodes</a>
        <a href="/docs">Documents</a>
        <a href="/gallery">Gallery</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <div class="hero-section">
        <div class="parallax-bg"></div>
        <h1 class="title">Living with the Ghost of Sam</h1>
        <p class="tagline">When the past won't stay dead... and has a wicked sense of humor</p>
      </div>

      <section class="synopsis-content">
        <div class="synopsis-card show-concept">
          <h2>Show Concept</h2>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p>"Living with the Ghost of Sam" is a darkly comedic supernatural drama that follows Derek Kinison and his wife Nancy Hammond as they inherit a mysterious Victorian mansion with connections to Derek's late cousin, legendary comedian Sam Kinison. After a dramatic corporate meltdown where Derek channels Sam's infamous comedic style, the couple discovers Ravencrest Mansion‚Äîa former psychiatric hospital turned comedy club with a hidden supernatural history.</p>
            <p>As Derek and Nancy renovate the mansion, they discover Sam's ghost haunts the property, manifesting through mirrors, self-playing pipe organs, and supernatural occurrences. The mansion itself seems sentient, responding to Derek's connection to Sam through mysterious dumbwaiters, weather phenomena, and time-bending architecture.</p>
            <p>What begins as a life reset for the couple evolves into a supernatural adventure as they uncover the mansion's secrets, navigate the eccentric townsfolk, and learn that Sam's final performance was more than just comedy‚Äîit was part of an elaborate ritual involving quantum consciousness technology that continues to affect the present.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="synopsis-card tone-style">
          <h2>Tone & Style</h2>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p>The series blends supernatural mystery with dark comedy, creating a unique tonal blend that echoes shows like "Dead to Me," "Russian Doll," and "What We Do in the Shadows" while incorporating elements of "The Haunting of Hill House" and "Locke & Key."</p>
            <p>The supernatural elements are played with both humor and genuine suspense, creating moments of comedic relief alongside legitimate scares. Sam's ghost embodies this duality‚Äîhilarious one moment, unsettling the next, always unpredictable.</p>
            <p>Visually, the show contrasts the modern world with the timeless Victorian architecture of Ravencrest, using shadow play, reflections, and subtle visual effects to blur the line between the natural and supernatural.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="key-themes">
          <h2>Key Themes</h2>
          <div class="theme-grid">
            <div class="theme">
              <div class="theme-icon">üè†</div>
              <h3>Finding Home</h3>
              <p>Derek and Nancy's journey to create a meaningful life outside the corporate rat race.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="theme">
              <div class="theme-icon">üé≠</div>
              <h3>Legacy & Identity</h3>
              <p>Derek's complex relationship with Sam's comedic legacy and his own identity.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="theme">
              <div class="theme-icon">üí´</div>
              <h3>Supernatural vs. Technology</h3>
              <p>The blurring line between advanced technology and supernatural phenomena.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="theme">
              <div class="theme-icon">üåÄ</div>
              <h3>Past & Present</h3>
              <p>How the past continues to influence the present through memory and connection.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="character-glimpse">
          <h2>Main Characters</h2>
          <div class="character-slider">
            <div class="character">
              <div class="character-image derek"></div>
              <h3>Derek Kinison</h3>
              <p>Former corporate executive who channels his cousin Sam's comedic energy during a breakdown, leading to a complete life change.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="character">
              <div class="character-image nancy"></div>
              <h3>Nancy Hammond</h3>
              <p>Art gallery owner balancing skepticism with growing acceptance of supernatural events while supporting Derek's transformation.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="character">
              <div class="character-image sam"></div>
              <h3>Sam Kinison's Ghost</h3>
              <p>The legendary comedian's spirit manifests through reflections, technological glitches, and architectural anomalies, guiding and challenging Derek.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="character">
              <div class="character-image linda"></div>
              <h3>Linda Rhodes</h3>
              <p>Mysterious realtor with supernatural connections who serves as gatekeeper between the town's secretive council and newcomers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="season-arc">
          <h2>Season One Arc</h2>
          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-node">
              <div class="node"></div>
              <div class="node-content">
                <h3>Setup (Episodes 1-3)</h3>
                <p>Derek and Nancy win the mansion in a supernatural contest and discover its connection to Sam's final days.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-node">
              <div class="node"></div>
              <div class="node-content">
                <h3>Discovery (Episodes 4-6)</h3>
                <p>The couple learns about the mansion's technological/supernatural hybrid nature and the mysterious disappearance of visitors.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-node">
              <div class="node"></div>
              <div class="node-content">
                <h3>Crisis (Episodes 7-9)</h3>
                <p>Corporate and supernatural worlds collide as the town council's true intentions are revealed.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-node">
              <div class="node"></div>
              <div class="node-content">
                <h3>Resolution (Episode 10)</h3>
                <p>Derek must perform Sam's final routine exactly to prevent an ancient alien technology from awakening.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="final-pitch">
          <h2>The Laugh Asylum Awaits...</h2>
          <p>"Living with the Ghost of Sam" combines supernatural mystery, character-driven drama, and dark comedy in a unique package that explores how we cope with loss, legacy, and life changes. As Derek and Nancy renovate Ravencrest, they're also rebuilding their lives and relationship‚Äîwith some unexpected supernatural assistance.</p>
          <p>With each episode blending humor, horror, and heart, the series offers something for fans of multiple genres while creating its own distinctive voice in the supernatural comedy landscape.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Base Styles */
  :root {
    --primary: #6E01EF;
    --secondary: #FF5722;
    --dark: #151515;
    --light: #f5f5f5;
    --accent: #00E5FF;
    --gradient-bg: linear-gradient(135deg, #1A1A1A 0%, #303030 100%);
  }

  .synopsis-container {
    color: var(--light);
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
  }

  .nav-header {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    background: rgba(21, 21, 21, 0.8);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .nav-header nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .nav-header a {
    color: var(--light);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .nav-header a:after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 0;
    height: 2px;
    bottom: -5px;
    left: 0;
    background-color: var(--accent);
    transition: width 0.3s ease;
  }

  .nav-header a:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .nav-header a:hover:after {
    width: 100%;
  }

  main {
    padding-top: 60px;
  }

  /* Hero Section */
  .hero-section {
    position: relative;
    height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .parallax-bg {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-image: url('/images/mansion.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-attachment: fixed;
    filter: brightness(0.3);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .title {
    font-size: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--light) 0%, var(--accent) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.3);
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: slideUp 1s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.5s;
  }

  /* Synopsis Content */
  .synopsis-content {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .synopsis-card {
    background: var(--gradient-bg);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(50px);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .show-concept {
    animation-delay: 0.3s;
  }

  .tone-style {
    animation-delay: 0.6s;
  }

  .synopsis-card h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .synopsis-card h2:after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: -10px;
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .synopsis-card p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* Key Themes */
  .key-themes {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    transform: translateY(50px);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.9s;
  }

  .key-themes h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .key-themes h2:after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: -10px;
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .theme-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .theme {
    background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.5);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .theme:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .theme-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .theme h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* Character Glimpse */
  .character-glimpse {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    transform: translateY(50px);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 1.2s;
  }

  .character-glimpse h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .character-glimpse h2:after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: -10px;
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .character-slider {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .character {
    background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.5);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .character:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .character-image {
    height: 150px;
    width: 150px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .derek {
    background-image: url('/images/derek.jpg');
    background-color: #333; /* Fallback */
  }

  .nancy {
    background-image: url('/images/nancy.jpg');
    background-color: #333; /* Fallback */
  }

  .sam {
    background-image: url('/images/sam.jpg');
    background-color: #333; /* Fallback */
  }

  .linda {
    background-image: url('/images/linda.jpg');
    background-color: #333; /* Fallback */
  }

  .character h3 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .character p {
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Season Arc Timeline */
  .season-arc {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    transform: translateY(50px);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 1.5s;
  }

  .season-arc h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .season-arc h2:after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: -10px;
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .timeline:before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 20px;
    height: 100%;
    width: 4px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .timeline-node {
    padding-left: 60px;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .node {
    position: absolute;
    left: 8px;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--dark);
    border: 4px solid var(--accent);
    top: 0;
  }

  .node-content {
    background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.5);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .node-content h3 {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* Final Pitch */
  .final-pitch {
    background: var(--gradient-bg);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transform: translateY(50px);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 1.8s;
  }

  .final-pitch h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .final-pitch p {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* Animations */
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  @keyframes slideUp {
    from {
      transform: translateY(30px);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      transform: translateY(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      transform: translateY(50px);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      transform: translateY(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  /* Media Queries */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .nav-header nav {
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .timeline:before {
      left: 15px;
    }

    .timeline-node {
      padding-left: 45px;
    }

    .node {
      left: 3px;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
    }

    .character-slider {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    }
  }

  /* For browsers that support it - cool scrollbar */
  ::-webkit-scrollbar {
    width: 10px;
  }

  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
    background: var(--dark);
  }

  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 5px;
  }

  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
    background: var(--primary);
  }

  /* Dark mode optimization */
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .synopsis-container {
      color: var(--light);
    }
  }

  /* Animation for page elements when they come into view */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .synopsis-card, .key-themes, .character-glimpse, .season-arc, .final-pitch {
      animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(50px);
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Intersection Observer for reveal animations
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('visible');
        }
      });
    }, {
      root: null,
      threshold: 0.1,
      rootMargin: '0px'
    });

    const sections = document.querySelectorAll('.synopsis-card, .key-themes, .character-glimpse, .season-arc, .final-pitch');
    sections.forEach(section => {
      observer.observe(section);
    });
  });

  // Parallax effect for hero background
  window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    const parallaxBg = document.querySelector('.parallax-bg');
    if (parallaxBg) {
      const scrollPosition = window.pageYOffset;
      parallaxBg.style.transform = `translateY(${scrollPosition * 0.5}px)`;
    }
  });
</script>
